loniki | ref = harv}}\n* {{cite journal | last = Stiernon | first = Lucien | title = Les origines du despotat d'\u00c9pire. \u00c0 propos d'un livre r\u00e9cent | trans-title = The origins of the Despotate of Epirus. On the occasion of a recent book | pages = 90\u2013126 | journal = Revue des \u00e9tudes byzantines | volume = 17 | year = 1959 | language = French | doi = 10.3406/rebyz.1959.1200 | url = http://www.persee.fr/doc/rebyz_0766-5598_1959_num_17_1_1200 | ref = harv}}\n* {{cite journal | last = Stiernon | first = Lucien | title = Les origines du despotat d'\u00c9pire. La date du couronnement de Th\u00e9odore Doukas | trans-title = The origins of the Despotate of Epirus. The date of the coronation of Theodore Doukas | pages = 197\u2013202 | journal = Actes du XII Congr\u00e8s international des \u00e9tudes byzantines | volume = II | location = Belgrade | year = 1964 | language = French | ref = harv}}\n* {{The Latin Renovatio of Byzantium}}\n* {{\u0397 \u0393\u03b5\u03bd\u03b5\u03b1\u03bb\u03bf\u03b3\u03af\u03b1 \u03c4\u03c9\u03bd \u039a\u03bf\u03bc\u03bd\u03b7\u03bd\u03ce\u03bd | volume = B}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{cite book | first = Fran\u00e7ois | last = Bredenkamp | title = The Byzantine Empire of Thessaloniki (1224\u20131242) | location = Thessaloniki | year = 1996 | publisher = Thessaloniki History Center |isbn=978-960-8433-17-5}}\n* {{cite journal | last = Fundic | first = Leonela | title = Art and Political Ideology in the State of Epiros During the Reign of Theodore Doukas (r. 1215\u20131230) | journal = Byzantina Symmeikta | volume = 23 | year = 2013 | pages = 217\u2013250 | url = https://www.academia.edu/6305185/Art_and_Political_Ideology_in_the_State_of_Epiros_During_the_Reign_of_Theodore_Doukas_r._1215-1230_Byzantina_Symmeikta_23_2013_217-250 }}\n* {{cite journal | first = Alkmini | last = Stavridou-Zafraka | title = The Empire of Thessaloniki (1224\u20131242). Political Ideology and Reality | journal = Vyzantiaka | volume = 19 | year = 1999 |